<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(الْمَسْأَلَة السَّابِعَة بعد الثلثمائة: شز.)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>مُبَاح الدَّم إِذا التجأ إِلَى الْحرم.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الْمَذْهَب:</span> لَا يعصمه.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">عِنْدهم:</span> يعصمه <span class="c2">(وَلَكِن ألجئ إِلَى الْإِخْرَاج)</span> .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الدَّلِيل من الْمَنْقُول:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">لنا:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ النَّبِي عَلَيْهِ السَّلَام:</span> <span class="c1">" الْحرم لَا يعيذ عَاصِيا وَلَا فَارًّا بخربة وَلَا دم "</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">لَهُم:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">قَوْله تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{أَو لم يرَوا أَنا جعلنَا حرما آمنا ... ...}</span> الْآيَة، والأمن إِنَّمَا يكون للخائف،<span class="c5"> وَقَوله تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{وَمن دخله كَانَ آمنا}</span> إِشَارَة لى من<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>